chment-3506045" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3506045" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/baldurs-gate-3-actors-want-more-dungeons-and-dragons-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3506045" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p> “我很受诱惑，伙计，”纽邦回答道。 “我不知道我们是否能够再次这样做，但我非常想再次这样做。那简直太好了。</p><p> “我认为人们必须向拉里安请愿才能再次实现这一目标，因为这是实现这一目标的唯一途径。但那就太好了。”</p><p> “拉里安让这一切发生，拉里安！”所罗门补充道。 “‘拉里安让这一切发生。’他的话，他现在有麻烦了，”纽邦开玩笑说，然后转移话题，这样观看直播的人就不会“破坏互联网”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-pokemon-company">神奇宝贝公司</a>透露了与梵高博物馆的合作伙伴关系， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pokemon-and-van-gogh-museum-reveal-limited-edition-pikachu-card-3505908">将神奇宝贝介绍给画家的作品，以鼓励和教育年轻艺术家</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-actors-urges-fans-to-petition-for-more-dungeons-dragons-3506015">《博德之门 3》演员们呼吁粉丝“请愿”更多《龙与地下城》</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ;
